{"tid":1088442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"還原靚靚！女神朱千雪搣走脂肪晒仙氣","createTime":"2019-04-02T05:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T07:28:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4523fdafde310858cdc2aecd5a7df21be8f33a","tid":1088442,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190331/photo/bkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190331095822\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190331095822&h=b9885d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩！呢個牛仔褸、呢個跌膊、呢個Filter&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n藝人朱千雪雖然依家以學業為重，不過間唔中都會出吓活動同大家見面，等一班粉絲唔使心掛掛。早前千雪就自嘲自己上鏡肥，仲話皆因自己太鍾意食嘢，呢日佢喺網上晒出多張個人照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190331/photo/bkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190331095822\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190331095822&h=38ad38a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190331/photo/bkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190331095822\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190331094503541-0331_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190331095822&h=09b50fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢着上黑色背心襯牛仔多套，露出少許膊頭，仲擺出多個表情，又嚟個側面甫同遮面甫，充滿電時續航力長達 482 公里， 足夠來回中環灣仔繞道 100 次，好似拍緊寫真一樣，似乎佢呢個周未過得好開心！好多網民都讚佢塊面一啲都唔肥，又大讚呢啲相都幾有味道喎～"},{"pid":"5320d976a6e8110ce15dbd1750b223e264227172","tid":1088442,"uid":54415,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"第三張filter到好似東凛"},{"pid":"00a43b65af8b4ab042ee663e5592cd3518098ca0","tid":1088442,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0